@fionajw @PaulaKrieg @becky_k_warren @fee @SamHartburn @MurrayH83 It seems you are all having fun! 😃 Have you tried the Zip command: https://t.co/2UlpMjh9QR 

You can also create lists:

A=(0,0)
B=(2,0)
C=(0,2)
L=Sequence(k, k, 1, 10)
T=Zip(Zip(Translate(Circle(A,2),Vector(m*Vector(A,B)+n*Vector(A,C))),m,L),n,L) https://t.co/PS0zjC9Agz
